All files contained in this torrent are in pdf, either originally in pdf, or converted from epub/azw3/mobi/etc. Please note that Calibre converts into pdf with a default text size much bigger than average, thus, if this is a concern to you, I suggest you download the epub collection instead and reconvert them to pdf. The following books could not be found: 
The Unfortunates - William Baer
The Outlaws - Ernst Von Salomon
Origins and Doctrine of Fascism - Giovanni Gentile
The Institutes of Biblical Law - Roushas Rushdoony
The Counter-revolution - Thomas Molnar

If you can find an ebook of any of these in any format, I would greatly appreciate you getting it to me via a comment to this torrent.
